Cappuccino
    - Sugar: Mandatory
        - Units: user choice
        - Assumptions: 
            - Units will be selectable between 1 and 5
    - Beans
        - Units: 5
    - Milk: Mandatory
        - Units: 3

Coffee
    - Sugar: Optional
        - Units: user choice
        - Assumptions: 
            - Units will be selectable between 1 and 5
    - Beans
        - Units: 2
    - Milk: Optional
        - Units: 1

Latte
    - Sugar: Optional
        - Units: user choice
        - Assumptions: 
            - Units will be selectable between 1 and 5
    - Beans
        - Units: 3
    - Milk: Mandatory
        - Units: 2

